title: 10 anniversary gifts
body: So the new 10 year gift with the Riot Kayle skin.... I know for a fact I didn't own Riot Kayle. I looked in my Kayle skins and I have her. But I didn't get a notification in the client. I don't have the summoner icon, though. I'm confused

replies.body: Yeah i owned Kayle and Riot Kayle....  I was worried when all my friends recieved stuff and i didn't haha

Per our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-), gifts are being sent out individually and you may not see a pop up toast for it.  It may take some time for all the gifts to finish being sent out, so hang tight until this is all done!
